info.title: Music Commands - Manual Setup
info.description:
Configurable options (Text Channel name and Category) can be found in the top left corner, within the green box

**PLEASE NOTE** This bot version requires you to type **"!musicsetup"** (the prefix is fixed as "!" for the restart to wor) for the setup to be initiated and will happen on a per server basis.
